                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1800696/">龙泉冢</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-04-17</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">美国并不完美，但她的历史令人感到激动，感到有一面旗还飘扬在空中。很难给这本书定性，它是有偏见的，也是有感情的，更是混杂的，但这不正是司马迁那种史学的伟大传统吗？</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="379837914">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-379837914" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-379837914" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="379837914">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cooltree/">Cooltree</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2011-04-20</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">中译本的排版实在是不怎么样。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="890572333">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-890572333" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-890572333" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="890572333">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/varro/">varro</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-02-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">以前没觉得作为通史作者的方纳有多厉害，最近细读了内战前的部分，真心叹服。章节论题划分得当，语言精炼而不失文采，雅俗共赏，鸿篇巨制中几乎没有一句废话。通史写到这个份上，可谓炉火纯青了。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="728170788">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-728170788" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-728170788" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="728170788">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jinfeixing/">孔劼</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2013-10-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">优点是通俗易懂，缺点是每节太小，显得琐碎。总体内容显得不伦不类，写了太多黑人与少数族裔的情况，又不是社会史。没有地图，很多地方光靠文字不能太理解形势。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

